title: Fantasy Extravaganza 2018!
itunes:title: Fantasy Extravaganza 2018!
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler & Chris Wesseling - take a quick glimpse at the latest news (5:00), before welcoming in Marcas Grant for their 4th Annual Fantasy Extravaganza (23:00). The heroes discuss #BSOHL (Best Shape Of His Life) (28:30), their choices for sleepers (38:00) and “not on my team.” They make a few stops at Sizzler’s Fantasy Corner and close with their best draft day advice (52:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
